Celestial Agent serves the Lifebane King and impersonates people of significant importance to acquire power, wealth, and land, her last imitation to the Lifebane King is that to mimic his wife to rekindle his broken heart. However, the Lifebane King’s mind slowly corrodes into madness by the poisoned waters of which she shared lip-to-lip. Her mind shattered, scattering in the four winds, her persona: anger, sadness, happiness, and envy.

                Anger: Disliking the Queen being weak
                Sadness: She couldn’t save the Lifebane King
                Happiness: When she received compliments and piercing gaze of the Lifebane King
                Envy: Wished the Lifebane King only saw her with his gaze 
